{"id":294062,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-8名蒙冤警察被关久敬庄见证湖北访民被殴/","date":"2013-05-18T01:45:47Z","modified":"2013-05-18T01:45:47Z","title":"维权网 | 8名蒙冤警察被关久敬庄见证湖北访民被殴打截访（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>点</span><span>，在北京的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名蒙冤警察来到中纪委门前，准备进入中纪委大门对贪腐官员实名举报。不想，却遭到北京治安总队福绥境派出所拦截并被强行送到久敬庄。约一个小时半后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名蒙冤警察被久敬庄工作人员释放，回到住处。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名蒙冤警察分别是辽宁沈阳马治国、赵宏炎、吴晓东，辽宁抚顺葛利元，黑龙江徐兆杰，湖北黄玲，河北周历，贵州邓朝霞。他们在久敬庄滞留期间，还见到一对来自湖北鄂州的访民夫妻廖建新和他的妻子余福意被四名黑保安殴打，廖建新还被黑保安撕破了白衣衫。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分左右，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名蒙冤警察被久敬庄工作人员释放后，其中湖北蒙冤警察黄玲和一位湖北维权人士邹四新一起护送廖建新、余福意夫妻。刚出久敬庄，就在门前遭到一伙不明身份人士暴力截访，廖建新、余福意夫妻被强行推上一辆车牌号为：京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">E52299</span><span>，当场开车走了。黄玲和邹四新两位女士只能望着汽车远去而无能为力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，本网信息员根据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名蒙冤警察提供廖建新的手机致电采访廖建新，据廖说：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>下午，他和妻子是被湖北驻京办工作人员当天带回了湖北鄂州。当晚在当地派出所做完笔录并被警告一番后获释。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据廖建新说，他是湖北省鄂州市仕屋村人，因为去年政府征地补偿欠透明和不足而上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>廖建新手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13297694059</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_oEvwNurU4U/UZZX1nc9T2I/AAAAAAAAiII/aYcynuq4XYI/s1600/01.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_oEvwNurU4U/UZZX1nc9T2I/AAAAAAAAiII/aYcynuq4XYI/s320/01.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名蒙冤警察在久敬庄</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-KB-Yb3KoWJk/UZZYKY9hqiI/AAAAAAAAiIY/x3bNPks4Ykg/s1600/02.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-KB-Yb3KoWJk/UZZYKY9hqiI/AAAAAAAAiIY/x3bNPks4Ykg/s320/02.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-IqwX4Wu0grM/UZZYId8rVPI/AAAAAAAAiIQ/sCQGRXRfr74/s1600/03.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-IqwX4Wu0grM/UZZYId8rVPI/AAAAAAAAiIQ/sCQGRXRfr74/s320/03.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>廖建新被殴打撕破的上衣</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}